    Why Choose Our Polycarbonate Windows?

    Industry-leading technology backed by decades of manufacturing excellence

    Fusionite Coatings
    Unmatched scratch resistance, UV protection, and anti-fog properties that outlast the competition.
    2-Week Prototypes
    From CAD to delivery custom prototypes tailored to your exact specifications.
    Full Compliance
    USDOT, ECE R43, ISO, ANSI certified for critical-use applications.
    Complex Shapes
    The only manufacturer capable of complex formed shapes with advanced coatings.

    Complete In-House Capabilities

    From coating to delivery everything happens under one roof for faster turnaround and tighter quality control

    Substrate Enhancement

    Advanced coating and laminating processes

    Laminating
    Bullet-Resistant Multilayer Windows
    PVB interlayer technology that absorbs impact energy. Ideal for military, security, and high-risk applications.
    Hard Coating
    Application-Specific Optical Coatings
    Scratch-resistant, anti-fog, anti-static, anti-glare, UV-resistant, and chemical-resistant coatings tailored to your specs.
    Screen Printing
    Custom Blackout (Frit) Patterns
    Unlimited frit patterns on sheets up to 5 12. Multi-color inks compatible with silicone hard coats.

    Window Fabricating

    Precision forming and machining

    Drape Forming
    Complex Shapes with Minimal Distortion
    Proprietary forming for any size from helmet faceshields to massive windshields.
    CNC Machining
    Superior Edge Quality, Quickly
    Large-format 3, 5, and 6-axis CNC machining with in-house tooling design.
    Etching
    Custom Window Engraving
    Laser etching and CNC routing for logos, VINs, and certification labels.

    Finishing Services

    Testing, assembly, and logistics

    Assembly
    Complete Product Assembly
    Hardware integration, custom packaging, and kitting ready to install.
    Testing
    Guaranteed Quality
    On-site ASTM lab testing for optical clarity, adhesion, durability, and cosmetics.
    Fulfillment
    Logistics & Distribution Support
    End-to-end logistics management. Components arrive on time and defect-free.
